            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/745/919.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 03:45:32 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 1 月 18 日消息，据“小米商城”官方微博，小米商城今天上架“非凡礼盒”及“热爱礼盒”手机套装，<span class="accentTextColor">各限量&nbsp;3000&nbsp;套</span>，其中“非凡礼盒”对应小米&nbsp;13/14&nbsp;手机、“热爱礼盒”对应&nbsp;Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro&nbsp;系列手机。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="530" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/2769d975-eb35-4522-befb-13ec2493b667.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE5NC5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_19,x_19,a_0/format,f_auto" title="小米 13/14、Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro 手机新增“非凡礼盒”及“热爱礼盒”套装，含拼装积木充电宝等" width="1262" /></p><p>IT之家整理具体礼盒信息如下：</p><h3>“非凡礼盒”套装</h3><p>购买小米&nbsp;13/14&nbsp;手机任意版本，<span class="accentTextColor">另加&nbsp;189&nbsp;元升级“非凡礼盒”套装</span>，套装内含：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>小米&nbsp;13/14&nbsp;手机</p></li><li><p>定制 CyberDog2&nbsp;拼装积木</p></li><li><p>定制碳纤维纹理保护壳</p></li></ul><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1732" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/8c4f53e8-c413-43c2-ab48-f8cd5b9a520b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="小米 13/14、Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro 手机新增“非凡礼盒”及“热爱礼盒”套装，含拼装积木充电宝等" width="640" /></p><figcaption>▲ 图源“小米商城”官方微博（下同）</figcaption><h3>“热爱礼盒”套装</h3><p>购买 Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro&nbsp;系列手机任意版本，<span class="accentTextColor">另加&nbsp;139&nbsp;元升级“热爱礼盒”套装</span>，套装内含：</p><ul class="ai-word-checked list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro&nbsp;手机</p></li><li><p>定制潮流手机包</p></li><li><p>小米充电宝&nbsp;10000&nbsp;毫安时&nbsp;22.5W</p></li></ul><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2409" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/d81bcfb3-c846-4c62-9bc6-a09cf9114748.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="小米 13/14、Redmi K70 / Note 13 Pro 手机新增“非凡礼盒”及“热爱礼盒”套装，含拼装积木充电宝等" width="1280" /></p><p>IT之家另附价格信息如下：</p><h3>“非凡礼盒”套装价格</h3><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><a href="https://c.duomai.com/track.php?site_id=157062&amp;aid=4705&amp;euid=&amp;t=https%3a%2f%2fwww.mi.com%2fshop%2fbuy%2